          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 pb-lg-0 pb-6">
              <div class="text-lg-start text-center font-zaux2 zaux-theme--light2 pb-3 pb-lg-4">
                  <h6 class="fw-demi c-typo-fs-10 c-typo-fs-lg-16">Innovation, Prevention, Preparedness</h6>
              </div>
              <div class="c-typo-style1-4 c-typo-style1-lg-8">
                <p>The ERA 2022 Congress in Paris will take place from May 19 to 22, 2022 as a hybrid event, thus being both live and virtual, with speakers, chairs and delegates attending live and remotely.</p>
                <p>The Congress programme is now online and guarantees, both live and virtual, top-quality presentations,
                  and a close interaction with the attendees.</p>
                <p>For any queries regarding the programme, please send an e-mail to <strong>program@era-online.or</strong></p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 d-flex">
           <div class="maw-f400 m-auto">
              <div class="border-gradient px-4">
                <div class="text-center zaux-theme--light1 pt-7 pb-8">
                  <div class="font-zaux2 pb-4">
                    <h6 class="fw-demi c-typo-fs-8 c-typo-fs-lg-10">Programme at a glance</h6>
                  </div>
                  <div class="c-typo-style1-4 c-typo-style1-lg-8 pb-6">
                    <p>The preliminary programme is now availble for download.<p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="">
                    <a class="c-cta1 c-cta1--sm c-cta1--red" href="#" title="button title">Download</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <!-- end row -->
        </div>


      <div class="zaux-theme--light2">

        <!-- start row -->
        <div class="row gx-3">
           {% set total = 4 %}
           {% set _htmlCardContent %}
          <div class="card1__head zaux-theme--dark1">
